headline: GoDaddy Creates Trusted Identity Naming System for AI Agents
summary: AI agents are launching at an incredibly rapid pace, with more than one billion agents projected to be built by businesses alone in the next three years. As AI agents start communicating with one another, a major challenge is suddenly emerging: there is currently no standard for distinguishing legitimate agents from unvetted or malicious ones, nor enforcing the integrity of agent-to-agent interactions.
